<help communications shout>

Broadcasts a message to everyone awake in your current zone.
Think of it as similar to a yell, ie don't go blathering off all the
time and annoy ppl!

Syntax:  shout [your message]

Example:  shout I'm lost, please help me!

<color=red>
See Also:  channels, tell, say, emote
</color></help>
